(214, '<p class=\"m-0\">Turn your Profile Page into a hub of Customer Engagement and Experience. Showcase\r\n                        your upcoming products, featured products and their ratings, What’s trending apart from verified\r\n                        contact details. Conduct Surveys, Polls to ascertain customer pulse. Establish deep continuous\r\n                        connect with your verified customers to retain them till perpetuity.</p>', NULL, 'upcoming'),
(215, '<p class=\"m-0\">Latest AI technology would bring continuous customer insights both prescriptive and\r\n                        predictive. Voice, Video and Emotion AI would crystalize insights never seen before thereby\r\n                        giving your organisation a crucial edge at a fraction of the current cost incurred.</p>', NULL, 'upcoming');
