(1, 1, 'bannner_content', '<h1>India\'s Premier</h1>\r\n<h2>Customer Experience Platform</h2>'),
(2, 1, 'for_business', '<h2 class=\"main-head\"><small>Why join Bolo Grahak</small> <br>For Business/Organisaton</h2>\r\n            <div class=\"common-ul\">\r\n              <ul class=\"mb-0\">\r\n                <li>Turn into a Hub of Customer Experience and Engagement</li>\r\n                <li>Showcase your featured products and whats trending</li>\r\n                <li>Conduct Surveys, Polls to ascertain Customer pulse </li>\r\n                <li>Establish deep continuous connect & retain your customers</li>\r\n                <li>Take advantage of latest in AI - Emotion, Voice, Video, Text AI</li>\r\n              </ul>\r\n            </div>'),
(3, 1, 'for_customer', '            <div class=\"all_features_home_page\">\r\n              <div class=\"heading_area\">\r\n                <h5>Features</h5>\r\n                <h2>For Grahak(Customer)</h2>\r\n              </div>\r\n              <div class=\"each_featur\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\r\n                Speak freely on your Customer experience, <strong class=\"zoom_animation\">#NeverStaySilent</strong>\r\n              </div>\r\n              <div class=\"each_featur\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\r\n                Know about your rights as <strong class=\"zoom_animation\">#CustomerRightsMatter</strong>\r\n              </div>\r\n              <div class=\"each_featur\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\r\n                All ages, communities, nations come together, <strong class=\"zoom_animation\">#BuildGlobalTrust</strong>\r\n              </div>\r\n              <div class=\"each_featur\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\r\n                Make Organizations listen and innovate. <strong class=\"zoom_animation\">#CustomersHavePower</strong>\r\n              </div>\r\n              <div class=\"each_featur\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">\r\n                Next-Gen AI technology powered. <strong class=\"zoom_animation\">#UltimateCustomerExperience</strong>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </div>'),
(4, 1, 'cus_right_content', '<h2 class=\"main-head\"><small>Know more About</small> <br> Grahak <span>Rights</span></h2>\r\n            <p>Consumer rights protect consumers/Grahak against unfair practices and enable them to enforce these rights. In India, The Consumer Protection Act was enacted on 24 December, 1986 and was updated on 6 August, 2019. It came into force in July 2020 to make sure that the rights of consumers in this country do not go unheard. This Act guarantees 6 basic rights to consumers.</p>\r\n            <div class=\"ul-50 common-ul\">\r\n              <ul>\r\n                <li>Right to Safety</li>\r\n                <li>Right to be Heard</li>\r\n                <li>Right to be Informed</li>\r\n                <li>Right to Seek redressal</li>\r\n                <li>Right to Choose</li>\r\n                <li>Right to Consumer Education</li>\r\n              </ul>\r\n            </div>'),
