(16, 1, 'about_us_content', '<h2 class=\"main-head\"><span>About</span> Us</h2>\r\n            <p><strong>Bolo Grahak is a platform for all consumers, citizens, visitors to share their shopping, visit and other experiences and give feedback on all products and services. Our mission is to help businesses, institutes, organizations listen, act and continuously improve their offerings to better meet the needs of their customers.</strong> </p>\r\n            <p><strong>Our platform provides a fluid and transparent environment with no pre-moderation, so that people can share their opinions and build trust.</strong></p>\r\n<h4>Join us now to experience the difference!</h4>'),
