(64, 3, 'bannner_content', '<h3 class=\"business-cur-head mb-3\"><sup><i class=\"fa-solid fa-quote-left\"></i></sup>The best\r\n                        business insights often lie hidden in customer feedback<sup><i\r\n                              class=\"fa-solid fa-quote-right\"></i></sup></h3>\r\n                     <p><span id=\"type-writing\"><noscript>But for most companies, comments and feedbacks require too\r\n                              much of the organization’s resources to dissect and analyse. To make sense of the customer\r\n                              feedback data across company website, call centre software, Facebook, Google Review,\r\n                              Twitter and emails at Customer Support, organizations have traditionally employed either\r\n                              manual analysis processes by outside expensive experts or used siloed text analytics\r\n                              solutions which does not give the holistic picture. Employees who actually interact with\r\n                              customers typically aren’t able to effectively capture and report the feedback thereby\r\n                              leading to customers being lost before the company is able to analyse and do course\r\n                              correction. With artificial intelligence doing the heavy lifting, BoloGrahak’s fully\r\n                              integrated, seamless and effortless solution provides real-time trends and insights from\r\n                              customer feedback, accessible across every customer touchpoint so that your employees can\r\n                              use this information to improve customer satisfaction and loyalty.</noscript></span></p>'),
(65, 3, 'features_title', 'Features'),
(66, 3, 'advantage_title', 'Advantage'),
(67, 3, 'advantage_content', '<ul class=\"mb-0\">\r\n                           <li data-aos=\"fade-up\" data-aos-duration=\"1000\">Provide your prospects and customers with a\r\n                              <strong class=\"zoom_animation\" data-aos-duration=\"3000\">truly</strong> objective review of\r\n                              the quality of your offerings.\r\n                           </li>\r\n                           <li data-aos=\"fade-up\" data-aos-duration=\"4000\">Listen, act and continuously <strong\r\n                                 class=\"zoom_animation\">improve</strong> your offerings to better meet the needs of your\r\n                              customers.</li>\r\n                           <li data-aos=\"fade-up\" data-aos-duration=\"5000\">Retain, Attract, <strong\r\n                                 class=\"zoom_animation\">Expand</strong> on your Customer base.</li>\r\n                           <li data-aos=\"fade-up\" data-aos-duration=\"6000\">Easily collect and display <strong\r\n                                 class=\"zoom_animation\">real</strong> customer reviews across your website, social media\r\n                              pages, marketing campaigns and even offline locations.</li>\r\n                           <li data-aos=\"fade-up\" data-aos-duration=\"7000\"><strong\r\n                                 class=\"zoom_animation\">Increase</strong> conversions and sales by displaying Bolo\r\n                              Grahak reviews on your website with GrahakTrust widgets.</li>\r\n                        </ul>'),
(68, 3, 'dont_forget_title', 'Don’t <span>Forget To</span>'),
(69, 3, 'dont_forget_content_1', '<h4 class=\"zoom_animation\"><strong>Keep Customer First - Har Haal mein:</strong></h4>\r\n                     <p class=\"m-0\" data-aos=\"fade-up\">Upon receiving reviews, your customer service team reads and\r\n                        responds to each reviewer individually. The one-to-one communication allows you to resolve\r\n                        issues personally, improve your service and provide affirmation to happy customers.</p>'),
(70, 3, 'dont_forget_content_2', '<h4 class=\"zoom_animation\"><strong>Stay Ahead of Disruption:</strong></h4>\r\n                     <p class=\"m-0\" data-aos=\"zoom-in-left\" data-aos-delay=\"2500\">Your business should especially\r\n                        appreciate negative reviews because it will allow you to figure out what you are not doing well\r\n                        enough and improve (or else get disrupted by a competitor).</p>'),
(71, 3, 'did_you_know_title', 'Did <span>you know?</span>'),
(72, 3, 'did_you_know_content_1', '<p class=\"m-0\">People will choose a product with more reviews but lesser rating over a similar\r\n                           product with a higher rating but fewer reviews. <br> <span>Study from the Association for\r\n                              Psychological Science</span></p>'),
(73, 3, 'did_you_know_content_2', '<p class=\"m-0\">Review stars in search can improve click-through rates up to 35%. <br>\r\n                           <span>According to an original study by ConversionXL</span>\r\n                        </p>'),
